Memberships
Suwannee Valley Resort
offers a full-service, clothing optional resort that is perfect for the newbie or the veteran nudist. We know you may be hesitant... very few bodies are perfect, that’s okay.  You may be concerned that someone you know will see you naked...but they will be naked too...that’s okay.  You may be concerned about what happens at “one of those places”...that’s okay, because we promise you a safe and relaxing day, weekend, or extended stay.  We are an AANR and TNS compliant resort.
Amenities: Pool, Hot tub, Restaurant, Bar, Clubhouse,
we have it all...WE JUST NEED YOU!!!
*In addition we are a 21 and older resort.  No one under the age of 21 will be permitted into the park.
Rates
Effective January 1st, 2025
Day Memberships
7.5% sales tax not included in rates shown
Non Affiliated
You may visit up to 3 times on temp membership before membership in SVR, AANR or TNS is Required. After 3 visits AANR or TNS is required.
Single:
$37
Couple: $47
Veterans, Police, Fire & EMS Receive 10% Off Listed Price with proof of service with honorable discharge. Thank you for your service!
AANR & TNS Members
You may visit up to 3 times on temp membership before membership in SVR, AANR or TNS is Required. After 3 visits AANR or TNS is required. You can save money and join AANR through us, $44 pp/yr.
Single:
$27 (with AANR or TNS Membership
Couple: $37
(with AANR or TNS Membership
Veterans, Police, Fire & EMS Receive 10% Off Listed Price with proof of service with honorable discharge. Thank you for your service!
Proof of membership or service required to receive discounts. (Active H.D. or Retired). On Stay & Memberships
Full Memberships
No daily membership fees are paid when you are a full member at SVR
7.5% sales tax not included in rates shown
SVR Membership
Single:
$505 (plus tax)
Couple: $750 (plus tax)
Veterans, Police, Fire and EMS - SVR Membership
Single:
$455 (plus tax)
Couple: 680 (plus tax)
Proof of membership or service required to receive discounts. (Active H.D. or Retired)
You may also join AANR or TNS through SVR at the following annual rates:
AANR
(American Association of Nude Recreation) – Couple = $90.00, Single – $45.00 (when signing up at SVR)
TNS
(The Naturist Society) – Couple or Single = $79.00
SVR does not discriminate against race, color, religion, sex, national origin, disability or age. We also strongly follow AANR and TNS guidelines.

In addition we are a 21 and older resort. No one under the age of 21 will be permitted into the resort. Background checks are done on entering resort.
Testimonials
What our guests say...





5/5
"Spent the night there while traveling home up north. Everyone was very friendly and helpful. Showed us around being our first time there and showed us to our cabin.  We unpacked and ate our dinner at the picnic table in front of our rental. Felt very good to get our clothes off.  Next morning we sat outside and just enjoyed. We will be back on our next trip down south.".
Ron B.
